# <type>(<scope>): <subject>
#
# <body>
#
# <footer>
#
# --- CONVENTIONAL COMMITS ---
# Types:
#   feat:     New feature
#   fix:      Bug fix
#   docs:     Documentation only
#   style:    Formatting, no code change
#   refactor: Code change, no new feature or fix
#   perf:     Performance improvement
#   test:     Adding/updating tests
#   chore:    Build, config, tooling
#
# Scope (optional): component or area affected
#   e.g., color-utils, contrast-grid, theme
#
# Subject: imperative, lowercase, no period
#   e.g., "add color parser for hex format"
#
# Body (optional): explain what and why
#
# Footer (optional): breaking changes, issue refs
#   BREAKING CHANGE: <description>
#   Closes #123
#
# --- EXAMPLES ---
# feat(color-utils): add HSL color parsing
# fix(contrast-grid): correct ratio calculation for dark colors
# docs: update README with setup instructions
# chore: configure vite for production build
